                             |  Internet User         |
                             |  Requests www.example.com |
                             +-----------+------------+
                                         |
                            (1) DNS Lookup (Route 53)
                                         |
                                         v
                            +----------------------+
                            |  Internet Gateway (IGW) |
                            +----------------------+
