  rules:
  - host: www.example.com
    http:
      paths:
      - path: /
        pathType: Prefix
        backend:
          service:
            name: my-service
            port:
              number: 80
ğŸ”¹ 4. Kubernetes Service (LoadBalancer / NodePort / ClusterIP)
Forwards traffic to the correct Pod.

Uses labels and selectors to find the right Pod.

Example Service definition:

yaml
Copy
Edit
